review_blob: First beer Ive ever had. Many later and I still know that this beer bests any other. Germans make the best beer, period.

I am no expert on beer. I just started drinking it maybe once or twice a week to try the different ones. Let me be clear when I say this, its horrible. If you want something with a distinct and inviting flavor, throw this away. It really tastes like grain and socks. After drinking this, my mouth is really dry. Get some good beer from Europe that isnt brewed by InBev if you want to enjoy your alcoholic drink.
